 "title": "Frikkadelle – tomato bredie style",
 "excerpt": "Frikkadelle in their own time fill up a crowd. Tonight I was in the mood for tomato frikkadelle on mash. I know it's mashed potatoes but it just doesn't sound as filling as mash. YOU NEED: 700g mince 5 ml ground coriander 2.5 ml ground nutmeg 1 egg 2 slices of bread 80 ml milk …",
