  "title": "Frikkadelle - tomato bredie style - Marinda Kook",
  "description": null
 },
 "html": "<p>Frikkadelle in their own time fill up a crowd.  Tonight I was in the mood for tomato frikkadelle on mash.  I know it's mashed potatoes but it just doesn't sound as filling as mash.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-final-blog-014.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-945\" alt=\"frikadelle final blog 014\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-final-blog-014-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>YOU NEED:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>700g mince<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-001.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-929\" alt=\"frikadelle en soutvleis en mash blog 001\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-001-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>5 ml ground coriander</li>\n<li>2,5 ml ground nutmeg<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-006.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-947\" alt=\"frikadelle en soutvleis en mash blog 006\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-006-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>1 egg</li>\n<li>2 slices of bread<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-002.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-930\" alt=\"frikadelle en soutvleis en mash blog 002\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-002-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>80 ml milk</li>\n<li>1 onion</li>\n<li>6 garlic cloves</li>\n<li>1 sprig rosemary</li>\n<li>1 tin tomatoes</li>\n<li>1 packet tomato paste</li>\n<li>80 ml chutney</li>\n<li>60 ml Worcestershire sauce<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-028.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-948\" alt=\"frikadelle en soutvleis en mash blog 028\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-028-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>25 ml sugar</li>\n<li>salt and pepper to taste</li>\n</ul>\n<p>NOW:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>soak the bread in milk in a plate<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-003.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-931\" alt=\"frikadelle en soutvleis en mash blog 003\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-003-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>put the mince in a bowl and loosen it up with a fork<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-008.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-932\" alt=\"frikadelle en soutvleis en mash blog 008\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-008-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>sprinkle the nutmeg, coriander, salt and pepper over the mince<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-011.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-933\" alt=\"frikadelle en soutvleis en mash blog 011\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-011-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>squeeze the milk out of the bread and crumble the bread over the mince<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-012.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-934\" alt=\"frikadelle en soutvleis en mash blog 012\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-012-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>whisk the egg in a cup and add that to the mince too<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-014.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-935\" alt=\"frikadelle en soutvleis en mash blog 014\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-014-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>now you have to use your hands and mix everything thoroughly<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-016.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-936\" alt=\"frikadelle en soutvleis en mash blog 016\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-016-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>shape frikkadelle as big as you like and set aside<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-019.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-937\" alt=\"frikadelle en soutvleis en mash blog 019\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-019-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>slice your onion into an oven dish and add the garlic cloves and rosemary to the oven dish too<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-022.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-938\" alt=\"frikadelle en soutvleis en mash blog 022\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-022-768x1024.jpg\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></li>\n<li>pack the frikkadelle onto the onions in the oven dish<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-024.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-939\" alt=\"frikadelle en soutvleis en mash blog 024\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-024-768x1024.jpg\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></li>\n<li>mix the sauce for the frikkadelle in a bowl: tin of tomato, tomato paste, Worcestershire sauce, chutney, sugar, salt and pepper</li>\n<li>pour the sauce over the frikkadelle<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-035.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-942\" alt=\"frikadelle en soutvleis en mash blog 035\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-en-soutvleis-en-mash-blog-035-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>bake in the oven at 180 degrees Celsius covered with foil for 30 minutes</li>\n<li>remove the foil and bake uncovered now for another 30 minutes<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-final-blog-003.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-943\" alt=\"frikadelle final blog 003\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-final-blog-003-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Enjoy the little meatballs on creamy mash and ask for more if you feel like it.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-final-blog-025.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-946\" alt=\"frikadelle final blog 025\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/frikadelle-final-blog-025-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>",
 "recipe": null
}
